				\begin{document}$$R \sim \exp {(-\omega \Delta )}$$\end{document}R∼exp(-ωΔ), where \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
