				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\mathcal{H}_0$$\end{document}H0 regime) to the onset of an exponential growth (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
